== PayPal Sweep
  This script automates the withdrawal of the balance of a specified PayPal
  account to the confirmed bank account.

== Usage 
  paypal_sweep.rb -u [paypal username] -p [paypal password] [options]

  For help use: paypal_sweep -h

== Options
  -u, --user		The PayPal account username
  -p, --password	The PayPal password for specified account
  -s, --sweep       Complete the full balance withdrawal
  -h, --help        Displays script help

== Examples
  Display the account balance only:
  	paypal_sweep.rb -u paypal_user@gmail.com -p mysecretpassword

  Output and withdraw the full balance:
    paypal_sweep.rb -u paypal_user@gmail.com -p mysecretpassword --sweep

